**LatencyFogScanner**  
**Description:**  
Scans APIs for intermittent latency spikes masked by average performance — ideal for uncovering “foggy” instability.

```markdown
# LatencyFogScanner - Intermittent Spike Detection Tool

LatencyFogScanner detects hard-to-see performance drops by analyzing volatility and low-frequency spike bursts.

## Features
- Fog-level latency anomaly detection  
- Historical trend mapping  
- CSV / JSON reports

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/LatencyFogScanner.git
cd LatencyFogScanner
python monitor.py
